in some memorable looks. Check out &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/the-picture-show/2025/02/02/g-s1-46115/photos-see-all-the-red-carpet-looks-from-the-67th-grammy-awards" target="_blank"&gt;photos of these looks&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;ul class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;➡️ Here's the &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/02/nx-s1-5280335/2025-grammy-awards-full-list-nominees-and-winners" target="_blank"&gt;complete list of winners&lt;/a&gt; at the 67th Grammy Awards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;➡️ Before they were Grammy winners, they were Tiny Desk performers. Watch some of their shows &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/03/g-s1-45827/2025-grammy-awards-tiny-desk-concert" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-45785" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 3500;         --source-height: 1969;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3500x1969+0+364/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F5c%2F1c%2Fd5fa79d54460a611f95312ab7694%2Fcamillefarrahlenain-npr-edmonddede-47.jpg" class="img" alt="Tenor Chauncey Packer and Soprano Taylor J. White and members of Opera Lafayette, OperaCreole and Louisiana Philarmonic Orchetra rehearse Edmond Dede&amp;#039;s opera &amp;quot;Morgiane&amp;quot; at St Louis Cathedral on Jan. 24." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Tenor Chauncey Packer and Soprano Taylor J. White and members of Opera Lafayette, OperaCreole and Louisiana Philarmonic Orchetra rehearse Edmond Dede's opera "Morgiane" at St Louis Cathedral on Jan. 24.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Camille Farrah Lenain for NPR                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Composer Edmond Dédé completed possibly the oldest opera by a Black musician in 1887 but never got to perform it. Now, the &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/03/nx-s1-4868011/oldest-black-american-opera-premiere" target="_blank"&gt;nearly forgotten &lt;em&gt;Morgiane&lt;/em&gt; is premiering&lt;/a&gt; in Washington, D.C.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;In 2008, Cara Beth Rogers learned her brother died in a boating accident just weeks into her study abroad trip to Morocco. She soon found herself filled with overwhelming grief on a plane ride home. A stranger and unsung hero reached out to her midway through the flight in a way that &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/03/nx-s1-5279576/kindness-grief-stranger-plane" target="_blank"&gt;made the journey a little more bearable&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Researchers have found that texture can be just as important as taste when it comes to &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/01/nx-s1-5281436/not-too-hard-not-too-soft-rotting-fruit-is-just-right-for-fruit-fly-maggots" target="_blank"&gt;food preferences for fruit fly maggots&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/859721331/suzanne-nuyen"target="_blank"   &gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Suzanne Nuyen&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
